Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.20,0:01:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今后如果有需要帮忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.36,0:01:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还麻烦你多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.03,0:01:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此\N我们还那么客气干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.77,0:01:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.97,0:01:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.61,0:01:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些利用权势\N贪图私利的奸人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.68,0:02:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们神风队要替天行道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.11,0:02:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！快…快来人啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.29,0:02:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么人 可恶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.01,0:02:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢…慢着！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.04,0:02:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们要多少钱？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.81,0:02:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问了也没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.38,0:02:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第十五话\N火炎般暗杀集团\N神风队横行霸道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.96,0:02:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是人心惶惶啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.43,0:02:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦！什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.69,0:02:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说那个神风队吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.03,0:02:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近这个暗杀集团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.46,0:02:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一一袭击政府高官要员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.80,0:02:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过被杀的都有贪污嫌疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.54,0:03:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以有很多人都认为神风队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.81,0:03:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是为正义而战的一队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.98,0:03:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不是一群以正义为名 而做坏事的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.92,0:03:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.18,0:03:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神谷活心派的活人剑\N才是正义之剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.19,0:03:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦！看不出祢彦\N偶尔也会说些像样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.49,0:03:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼！偶尔两个字就免了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.09,0:03:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家来吃点心喽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.23,0:03:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 小绫 小雀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.56,0:03:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们快来吃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.57,0:03:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑哥哥吃点心喽！我们快去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.67,0:03:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩！好吃！好吃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.24,0:03:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惠姑娘烤的蕃薯\N真的好好吃耶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.78,0:03:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀！真不好意思 惠姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.55,0:03:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心你看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.12,0:03:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰姑娘吃蕃薯的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.15,0:03:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是和蕃薯很配呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.62,0:03:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像不像传说中的蕃薯姑娘？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.26,0:03:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？什么嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.50,0:04:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助你在笑什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.57,0:04:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之！左之助在吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.51,0:04:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔！左之！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我直接闯进来真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.88,0:04:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？这不是老师吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.91,0:04:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛慌慌张张的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.18,0:04:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我私塾的这个孩子\N突然喊肚子痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.39,0:04:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得左之你有医生朋友\N所以才赶紧带他来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.92,0:04:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是玄斋医生刚好不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.53,0:04:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷因公事出远门去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在家哟！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.30,0:04:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.44,0:04:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.61,0:04:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有发烧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰姑娘！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.41,0:04:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.61,0:04:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你准备一床棉被
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.28,0:04:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心麻烦你去烧锅热水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.55,0:04:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.28,0:04:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师 这位姑娘是医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.42,0:04:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！女医生啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.22,0:04:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,个性我不敢说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.56,0:05:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她的医术 我敢给你担保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.33,0:05:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.26,0:05:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,废话少说 快帮我抱这孩子躺下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.26,0:05:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少一副命令的口气 这八婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.20,0:05:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！不可以吵架 左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.14,0:05:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看啊！左之八成喜欢惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.41,0:05:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人在喃喃什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.17,0:05:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快！带进房里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.11,0:05:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是感激不尽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.58,0:05:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像吃坏肚子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.35,0:05:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经不碍事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.45,0:05:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微睡一下就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.29,0:05:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是帮了大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.49,0:05:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不知要如何感谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.79,0:05:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师我也帮你看看吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.89,0:05:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.93,0:05:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师你的脸色很不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.67,0:05:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我啊！我只是吃得不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.34,0:05:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实在是因为太穷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.11,0:05:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子已经没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.35,0:05:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.42,0:05:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！太好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.98,0:06:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师是私塾的老师吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.79,0:06:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他和我一样住在长屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.89,0:06:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本是位武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.59,0:06:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何流落到长屋\N这事我也没问过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.23,0:06:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果在以前就是流浪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.00,0:06:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他其实每日受雇干活\N过着清贫的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.77,0:06:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还开了家不收学费的私塾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.40,0:06:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教附近的孩子读书写字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.31,0:06:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好伟大喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.68,0:06:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 你怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.49,0:06:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只觉得那老师好像在哪见过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.49,0:06:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事 可能是我多心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.87,0:06:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您是要好身手的刺客吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.04,0:07:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今后对方为了自保都警备森严
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.75,0:07:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要像之前这么顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.35,0:07:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要加强神风队的战力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.35,0:07:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有人选？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.62,0:07:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像过去斩人拔刀斋\N轰动京城那样的刺客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.40,0:07:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了明治这时代\N这要求会不会太过份？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.97,0:07:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是有想到一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.80,0:07:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔！真有这样的人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.94,0:07:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他身手没退步的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.97,0:07:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起拔刀斋有过之而无不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.04,0:07:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好！就交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.34,0:07:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.61,0:08:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 今天晚上吃什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.15,0:08:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拔了颗好萝卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.88,0:08:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山芋拿来煮汤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.55,0:08:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再炒个青菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.12,0:08:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该会蛮丰盛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.05,0:08:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦！怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.36,0:08:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是昨天那位老师吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.90,0:08:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！老师 你也到旁边休息一下嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.91,0:08:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛那么拼命呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.04,0:08:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再一会就可告一段落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.88,0:08:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然跟左之助说的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那混蛋想做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.56,0:09:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然不凡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.59,0:09:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.03,0:09:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见！佐佐木老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…东马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.76,0:09:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是神东马吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下我放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.00,0:09:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的身手还是跟以前一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.77,0:09:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.97,0:09:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我们很快会再见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.84,0:09:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那先告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.88,0:09:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师 你还好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.58,0:09:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.39,0:09:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心你看到了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.99,0:10:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那老师的攻击快得看不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.49,0:10:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是火野派一刀流\N登峰造极的[紫电太刀]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫电太刀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.37,0:10:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让对手防守不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.14,0:10:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闪电般刺穿对手的暗杀剑法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.71,0:10:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那老师到底是何许人物？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.38,0:10:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在京城曾和他交手过一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.81,0:10:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？剑心吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.66,0:11:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时对手是一个名叫\N新撰组的恐怖剑客集团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.30,0:11:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来才知道 他是\N京都捕组组长佐佐木平八郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.67,0:11:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那老师是新撰组的剑客吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.28,0:11:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是人不可貌相啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.72,0:11:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚一个人喝真没意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.96,0:11:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久没跟老师喝一杯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.90,0:11:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.73,0:11:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那伙人是什么人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.88,0:12:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐木老师 前几天失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.35,0:12:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.55,0:12:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚叫我出来是为了什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.82,0:12:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在学火野一刀流时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已是师父级了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.66,0:12:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时我还只是初出茅庐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才一阵子不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的剑术已经这么高明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.87,0:12:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您过奖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.10,0:12:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这期间你杀了多少人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.17,0:12:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先前你使太刀的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.44,0:12:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确是杀人不眨眼的剑法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.57,0:12:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑本来就是用来斩人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.04,0:12:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的剑不也是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.88,0:12:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想不想再让拿起剑 畅快地斩人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.48,0:12:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是指暗杀吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.09,0:12:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维新政府轻视我们武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.59,0:12:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政府官员都是利用权势\N中饱私囊的奸人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.89,0:12:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要打击这种腐败的政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.43,0:12:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有暗杀才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.13,0:12:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能改变世界吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会用这把剑改变给你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该不想就这样终老一生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.68,0:13:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.91,0:13:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要再登上光明的舞台？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.71,0:13:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论有什么理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.35,0:13:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人者都光明不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.28,0:13:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能再做这种傻事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.79,0:13:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.22,0:13:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我已弃剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.52,0:13:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,私塾的孩子们\N才是我珍视的宝贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.10,0:13:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且藉着教育这些孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.13,0:13:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才能洗清我杀人无数的罪过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.71,0:13:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东马 我们应该不会再见面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢着！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.94,0:13:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们神风队要的东西\N是绝对逃不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.28,0:13:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.32,0:13:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何 都要你加入我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.93,0:14:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来和剑心一样\N对老师真要刮目相看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.04,0:14:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那后来老师怎么说？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.71,0:14:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他断然拒绝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.21,0:14:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那伙人绝非善类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来不知会做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！左之助！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.55,0:14:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也来帮忙一下嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.09,0:14:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别叫他了 惠姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.19,0:14:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫左之助帮忙打扫\N待会下大雨就麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.56,0:14:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,废话！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.39,0:14:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.80,0:14:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.07,0:14:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.50,0:14:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了！才刚到！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.20,0:14:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来！玄斋医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.51,0:14:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都还好吧？\N我最担心你们两个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.11,0:14:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你们这么有精神就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.91,0:14:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷！ 你真的那么担心我们吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.65,0:14:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然喽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.95,0:14:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是我的宝贝呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.86,0:15:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已弃剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.89,0:15:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在私塾的孩子们\N才是我珍视的宝贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.26,0:15:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.17,0:15:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.61,0:15:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？那家伙匆匆忙忙地？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.34,0:15:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 一定是不打扫 怕被爷爷骂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.71,0:15:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.65,0:15:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论用什么手段\N都要让你加入我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.46,0:15:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.46,0:15:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.63,0:15:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我写好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.23,0:15:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔！写得真快 菊松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.36,0:15:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里 拿来我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.03,0:15:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.71,0:15:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.35,0:16:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.29,0:16:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定好下个目标了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.83,0:16:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要跟我走？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.83,0:16:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.47,0:16:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.47,0:16:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菊松！发生什么事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.31,0:16:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师跟着一个奇怪的人走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.54,0:16:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？老师往哪边走？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往品川那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.48,0:16:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！那混蛋果然找到这里来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.33,0:16:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北村总议长！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.30,0:16:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们替天行道来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.24,0:16:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.24,0:16:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是神风队！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.64,0:16:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.73,0:17:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是神风队！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.23,0:17:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么！那伙人在哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.37,0:17:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在前面的小路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.35,0:17:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐木老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.72,0:17:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经不能回头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.32,0:17:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是无法舍弃剑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.67,0:17:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢着！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.67,0:18:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.01,0:18:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左…左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.81,0:18:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,私塾老师怎么可以拿那种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.45,0:18:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.19,0:18:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿孩子们相要胁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.42,0:18:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这没良心的混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.09,0:18:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相乐左之助决不原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.06,0:18:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢着！左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.86,0:18:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔别发抖了 快站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.50,0:18:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.20,0:18:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能帮你到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.47,0:18:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己的性命自己顾吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.91,0:18:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.55,0:18:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别跑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.12,0:18:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敢阻碍我神风队的行动 好大的胆量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.40,0:19:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.37,0:19:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.44,0:19:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对没武器的人拔剑\N不觉得可耻吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.14,0:19:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的对手应该是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.38,0:19:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村先生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.85,0:19:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿那逆刃刀 真是笑话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.15,0:19:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有趣！你们都别出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.69,0:19:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.33,0:19:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看招！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.08,0:19:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了！紫电太刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.39,0:19:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！那剑法！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.40,0:20:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等没人打扰时\N我们再一比高下吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.60,0:20:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时我的剑 一定会刺穿你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.71,0:20:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.65,0:20:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那男的剑法和老师你的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.13,0:20:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我也差点就送命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十年过得真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.67,0:20:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.31,0:20:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是当时的斩人拔刀斋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.94,0:20:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我舍弃了过去的名字来东京的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.61,0:20:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像你舍弃你的剑一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.25,0:21:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧！老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.08,0:21:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师的心愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.69,0:21:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和剑心不会让人来破坏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.42,0:21:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师的手已不是握剑的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.59,0:21:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是教孩子读书的重要的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.06,0:21:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你！左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.23,0:21:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓不论怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.57,0:21:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我决不再拿剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.74,0:21:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好
